build.apache	    Installs the "mkapachecert" script.

build.nessus	    Will modify /usr/local/nessus/sbin/nessus-adduser and add
		    the "-q" argument which will quietly create user "nessus"
		    with password "nessus".

build.crontab       Installs root's crontab.

build.mysql         Performs initial configuration of the MySQL database.

build.snortcenter   Installs the SENTINIX specific mksnortcentersensorcert.

